 * autotest Support: autotest support can now be used by -a option. When using autotest, one or more directories to be watched for changes can specify by the -w option.
 * Explicit test directory: An arbitrary directory can now be used as the test directory by specifying the directory as the last argument for testrunner commands.</notes>
